Base URL : http://localhost:5000/

Users: -----------------------------------------------
Base URL : http://localhost:5000/users
By Id : http://localhost:5000/users?id=
By email : http://localhost:5000/users?email=
By name : http://localhost:5000/users?name=

Posts: -----------------------------------------------
Base URL : http://localhost:5000/posts
By Title : http://localhost:5000/posts?q=
By Id : http://localhost:5000/posts?id=

Carts: -----------------------------------------------
By email : http://localhost:5000/carts/:email
By Product Id : http://localhost:5000/carts/products/:productId
